--AnsibleGalaxy
ansible-galaxy init nginx

nginx
├── defaults
│   └── main.yml
├── files
├── handlers
│   └── main.yml
├── meta
│   └── main.yml
├── README.md
├── tasks
│   └── main.yml
├── templates
├── tests
│   ├── inventory
│   └── test.yml
└── vars
    └── main.yml

- defaults
	- here we will maintain all constant variables ex company logo
- vars
	- Here all the variables will be there
- meta
	- Author details etc
- handlers
	- handler details
- files
	- It contains the file for copying like default(ubuntu for nginx install) or index.html
- templates
	- index.html.j2
- tasks
	- all tasks we write go here
